ad: Hello! I am pleased to offer my gifts of warmth and unconditional love to people who would be served by an hour-long platonic cuddle session. What do I mean by "Platonic"?This is non-sexual. We will be fully clothed. My energy feels like that of a loving mother, a soothing therapist, a reassuring friend. What do I mean by "Cuddle"?We sit/recline on a couch, with my arm around you//your arm around me. Breathing deeply together. Perhaps talking, perhaps not. Gentle, soothing touch. Perhaps some light massage to help you relax, or to help us connect. Many people are served by the joy of being held close in a loving, platonic embrace. It eases people into feeling comfortable with touch if they are recovering from trauma, or are unfamiliar with touch. Being held helps people to feel safe crying, releasing emotions, laughing, and feeling worthy and deserving of love, in its purest form. "Being held by Hannah helped me relax and feel what was going on in my heart." Why me?I am a mother, an experienced joy coach, and pretty much everyone I'm close with tells me that they are unusually comfortable with me. People love to open up to me, share pieces of themselves that have been hidden. I have a comfy body, and find it very natural to get snuggly with people. I have noticed that when I offer to snuggle people, they have told me that it is rare for them, and very healing, to get to be held in the way that I hold.How it works:You respond in an e-mail with: why you would be served by platonic cuddling, your name, your phone number, and a good time to call you. From there, we will discuss our intentions on the phone, and if we're on the same page, set up a time to meet. The cost?The cost for a one-hour session, including a 5-15 minute intro conversation, is $100. I require a $25 initial payment after our phone call to reserve my time. The rest can be paid at the completion of the session.
title: Professional Platonic Cuddler

ad: QR Code Link to This PostStressed? Tense? Surrender your body to a great massage. My approach is to attend to the entire body. I'll then apply a hot towel and remove the excess lotion followed by a dry towel. Then I'll have you turn over to lie on your back.
